Articles.Content:
Hi!
Well yes again a discord server.
I just started my server where we would like to focus on building vehicles. I’m looking for those engineers who like to step away from reality a bit and like to build other types of vehicles. Theme can be the near future, sci-fi, or any artistic craft vehicle that is different from the usual. But I also welcome those who are interested in the topic. I prefer quality to quantity. Give it a try and join us.
Send a private message and you will receive an invitation.

Greetings to everyone. AG 

Edited August 4, 2020 by AG-cs
